16:45.830 --> 16:48.458
Just come back to the library, Hannah.

16:49.210 --> 16:50.757
Come back to the poetry.

16:52.920 --> 16:53.921
Maybe.

16:55.220 --> 16:56.209
I'll take maybe.

17:00.260 --> 17:01.841
