17:17.030 --> 17:18.156
[Mr. Baker]
Honey?

17:19.160 --> 17:20.149
Honey?

17:22.450 --> 17:23.439
You okay?

17:27.580 --> 17:30.959
I was just thinking
it's a bad sign that we're...

17:31.050 --> 17:34.042
running out of
"Buy One, Get One Free" stickers.

17:35.470 --> 17:39.133
We can look at it as a bad sign or
we can consider it the world telling us

17:39.220 --> 17:41.848
we can never discount our way
to Walplex prices.

