19:59.650 --> 20:01.527
But did you have a sense?

20:02.030 --> 20:03.019
Mrs. Jensen.

20:03.110 --> 20:04.111
-Lainie.
-LaIn|e.

20:04.200 --> 20:05.269
Please.

20:07.620 --> 20:10.248
I know this is not the subject
of our meeting,

20:10.330 --> 20:12.821
but do you know
where your son is right now?

20:14.580 --> 20:16.207
I assume he's in class.

20:16.290 --> 20:17.416
He isn't.

20:17.500 --> 20:20.207
He walked out of school this morning
and hasn't come back.

20:21.630 --> 20:24.258
[Clay]
I may be crazy,
but I am not that crazy.

20:24.340 --> 20:26.046
People free solo it all the time.

20:26.140 --> 20:28.131
People who climb things,

20:28.220 --> 20:29.380
people who climb rocks...

20:29.470 --> 20:32.268
which is a ridiculous thing to do
if you aren't being chased by something.

20:32.390 --> 20:33.800
It's for beginners.

20:33.890 --> 20:36.142
I used to climb it with my brothers
when we were kids.

20:37.060 --> 20:38.061
Here.

20:38.150 --> 20:39.435
Take this, clip it on.

20:40.030 --> 20:41.145
It's chalk.

20:41.240 --> 20:43.105
Put it on your hands, like this.

20:44.700 --> 20:45.689
Or you'll slip.

20:47.240 --> 20:48.366
What?

20:48.450 --> 20:50.281
Come on, are you a man or not?

20:50.370 --> 20:51.246
Not!

20:51.750 --> 20:55.117
Most definitely not.
I grant you that, no question.

20:56.880 --> 20:57.869
I, uh...

20:59.250 --> 21:00.456
