21:01.670 --> 21:03.467
[Tony] It's an easy climb.

21:03.550 --> 21:06.292
All the answers you seek
are at the top of the cliff.

21:13.560 --> 21:16.017
[Ryan] The drag of your hand
across my chest

21:16.100 --> 21:18.307
Sparks a blaze
my lips cannot extinguish

21:19.320 --> 21:22.141
You, stubborn inferno

21:22.740 --> 21:26.528
You drive fast, and damn
the red lights for slowing you down

21:27.110 --> 21:30.614
You see my veins shake
at your first touch

21:31.200 --> 21:34.829
The power to move my blood
on your own accord

21:34.910 --> 21:36.992
The definition of heart

21:37.580 --> 21:39.662
And after the stick shift jerk

21:39.750 --> 21:41.490
I beg my skin to do tricks

21:41.590 --> 21:44.127
Like forget how good it feels
to lose control

21:44.220 --> 21:46.427
Between the burning house

21:46.510 --> 21:47.795
Of your hands

21:50.350 --> 21:51.999
[applause]

21:56.810 --> 21:57.799
Whoo!

22:04.780 --> 22:05.599
Hey.

22:06.700 --> 22:07.735
That was...

22:08.530 --> 22:09.815
intense.

22:10.620 --> 22:12.531
