Now try and slow your breath down.

23:33.320 --> 23:34.321
How do I do that?

23:34.910 --> 23:36.070
By breathing slower.

23:36.160 --> 23:39.652
What do I do about my heart,
which is about to explode out of my chest?

23:39.750 --> 23:40.614
[cell phone rings]

23:42.370 --> 23:43.371
Shit.

23:43.460 --> 23:44.996
You brought your phone on a climb?

23:45.960 --> 23:47.791
No, I brought my phone on a walk.

23:47.880 --> 23:49.507
That's my mom's ring.

23:50.880 --> 23:54.338
Be a good son
or plunge to the rocks below.

23:54.720 --> 23:56.597
Yeah. Thanks for the perspective.

23:56.850 --> 23:57.839
[ringing continues]

23:57.930 --> 24:00.012
[Hannah]
It must be poss/b/e
to swim in the ocean

24:00.100 --> 24:01.761
of the one you love without drowning.

24:02.690 --> 24:05.762
It must be poss/b/e to swim
without becoming water yourself

24:07.270 --> 24:09.647
I keep finding stones tied to my feet.

24:10.860 --> 24:11.940
Sorry, I just...

24:12.030 --> 24:13.520
Just keep going, keep going.

24:17.580 --> 24:19.036
-Jess, I...
-What?

24:19.120 --> 24:20.576
-WIhat?

24:20.660 --> 24:21.866
I-I can't right now.

24:21.960 --> 24:23.166
No, no, it's okay.

24:23.750 --> 24:25.035
Maybe if I helped a little?

24:25.130 --> 24:27.200
Oh, Jess, come on, look. I just...

24:29.090 --> 24:31.411
Maybe later.
I just don't want to right now.

24:37.720 --> 24:39.210
I don't do it for you anymore.

24:39.890 --> 24:41.630
-That's not it.
-It has to be.

24:44.350 --> 24:46.261
You don't think I'm pretty anymore.

24:46.480 --> 24:47.515
Jess.

24:48.320 --> 24:49.639
God, no, Jess.

24:50.730 --> 24:52.186
You're so beautiful.

24:54.110 --> 24:55.691
What's happening to us?

24:58.160 --> 24:59.400
It'll all be fine, okay?

25:01.040 --> 25:03.326
Once these stupid
fucking tapes are done.

25:06.540 --> 25:07.916
Can we at least get high?

25:11.170 --> 25:13.468
-You don't even smoke.
-Yeah, I do.

25:17.140 --> 25:18.129
Okay.

25:18.350 --> 25:19.715
[C/ay]
We are really freaking h/gh.

25:19.810 --> 25:21.300
