25:21.390 --> 25:23.176
Chalk your hands if they're sweaty.

25:24.480 --> 25:25.936
I can't really feel my arms.

25:26.020 --> 25:28.011
You gotta shake 'em out, one at a time.

25:28.110 --> 25:29.816
Get the blood moving, all right?

25:29.900 --> 25:31.856
