25:31.940 --> 25:33.487
Good. Good.

25:33.820 --> 25:35.060
We're getting closer.

25:35.150 --> 25:37.983
Remember, you gotta go slow
if you want to climb fast.

25:39.870 --> 25:40.939
All right.

25:45.160 --> 25:47.242
-Oh, shit!
-Ow! Gah!

25:47.330 --> 25:48.319
Shit!

25:48.420 --> 25:49.580
Oh, shit!

25:49.920 --> 25:51.126
What? What? I can't see!

25:51.210 --> 25:52.290
I lost a handhold.

25:52.880 --> 25:54.757
Give me a sec,
I've got to figure this out.

25:56.220 --> 25:57.289
[banging at door]

25:57.380 --> 25:59.541
[Lainie] Clay! Clay, are you here?

25:59.640 --> 26:00.709
Lainie?

26:01.600 --> 26:03.841
He's not here. He isn't here.

26:04.180 --> 26:06.262
Okay. Okay, calm down. What's going on?

26:06.350 --> 26:08.227
I left you a detailed message.

26:08.310 --> 26:09.550
The department secretary is 90.

26:09.650 --> 26:11.936
He walked out of school and disappeared.

26:12.020 --> 26:13.601
I'm sure he didn't disappear.

26:13.690 --> 26:15.681
He is not answering his cell, Matt.

26:15.940 --> 26:18.773
So he skipped school
to play basketball or go for a ride.

26:18.860 --> 26:19.906
He's missing, Matt!

26:19.990 --> 26:22.117
He's playing hooky. He's not missing.

26:22.200 --> 26:24.156
If you minimize this, I will lose it.

26:24.240 --> 26:25.366
Okay, okay.

26:25.660 --> 26:26.786
We'll find him.

26:27.500 --> 26:28.910
He can't have gone far.

26:35.010 --> 26:37.831
All right, I'm gonna throw this.
Grab it, pull yourself up.

26:40.090 --> 26:41.842
-Tony, I can't.
-Of course you can.

26:42.100 --> 26:43.465
One foot at a time.

26:43.760 --> 26:44.761
Come on.

26:45.310 --> 26:46.345
Oh...

26:48.520 --> 26:51.853
-Whoa! Ah! Okay.
-All right, you got it.

26:53.320 --> 26:55.470
There you go. [laughs]

26:55.570 --> 26:57.356
-There you go!
-[grunting]

26:59.780 --> 27:01.190
-[C|ay gasps]
-There you go!

27:01.700 --> 27:02.735
Oh, shit!

27:03.240 --> 27:04.275
Oh, man!

27:06.410 --> 27:08.071
Whoa! That was freaking amazing.

27:08.500 --> 27:10.320
Was it? Or was it fucking amazing?

27:11.330 --> 27:14.333
That was fucking amazing.

27:15.090 --> 27:16.626
