27:19.800 --> 27:20.789
Fuck!

27:23.600 --> 27:24.919
Fuck!

27:26.140 --> 27:28.722
Fuck!

27:29.310 --> 27:30.379
Yeah.

27:31.230 --> 27:32.936
I saw this YouTube video once

27:33.020 --> 27:35.147
where this guy in Spain
was walking on this crane.

27:35.230 --> 27:36.970
He had to be at least 15 stories.

27:37.070 --> 27:38.981
He's walking, walking, walking.

27:39.570 --> 27:42.482
And then he slips.
He lets out this loud scream.

27:42.570 --> 27:43.776
Seconds later, wham!

27:44.160 --> 27:45.195
Wham what?

27:46.990 --> 27:49.447
