but I'm pretty sure he died.

27:49.870 --> 27:50.780
Shit, Clay.

27:52.290 --> 27:53.245
Fuck.

27:56.670 --> 27:59.719
I never totally realized,
that's a really great word.

28:00.300 --> 28:01.335
It is, huh?

28:02.010 --> 28:02.829
Uh...

28:03.260 --> 28:04.249
You're bleeding.

28:08.270 --> 28:09.305
Fuck.

28:09.470 --> 28:10.971
[Hannah]
Wow, this is scary.
[chuckles]

28:16.610 --> 28:18.771
Today I am wearing lacy black underwear

28:19.780 --> 28:22.396
For the sole purpose of knowing
I am wearing them

28:24.820 --> 28:25.980
And underneath that

28:27.740 --> 28:30.152
I am absolutely naked

28:32.580 --> 28:33.786
And I've got skin

28:34.880 --> 28:37.531
Miles and miles of skin

28:39.420 --> 28:42.162
I've got skin to cover all my thoughts
like Saran Wrap

28:42.720 --> 28:43.675
That you can see through

28:43.760 --> 28:46.137
to what leftovers are inside
from the night before

28:47.930 --> 28:49.670
And despite what you might think

28:50.140 --> 28:51.676
My skin is soft

28:52.390 --> 28:53.379
And smooth

28:54.850 --> 28:55.976
And easily scarred

28:58.940 --> 29:00.771
But that doesn't matter, right?

29:01.440 --> 29:03.772
You don't care about how soft my skin is

29:04.910 --> 29:07.697
You just want to hear
about what my fingers do in the dark

29:09.870 --> 29:12.282
