is crack open windows

29:12.370 --> 29:14.611
So I can see
lightning through the clouds?

29:16.750 --> 29:19.127
What if all they crave
is a jungle gym to climb

29:19.210 --> 29:21.417
For a taste of fresher air?

29:23.760 --> 29:24.920
I C/ay]
You promised me

29:25.010 --> 29:26.966
the secrets are at the top of this rock.

29:27.050 --> 29:29.462
-I risked my life to get here.
-You wouldn't have died.

29:30.510 --> 29:31.966
You'd break a bunch of shit.

29:32.470 --> 29:33.676
[scoffs]

29:41.820 --> 29:43.185
I never thought about it.

29:44.990 --> 29:45.979
Dying.

29:47.450 --> 29:48.565
Until this year.

29:55.120 --> 29:56.576
Have you ever seen a dead body?

30:00.630 --> 30:02.291
I've been to a few funerals.

30:04.760 --> 30:06.375
