30:08.550 --> 30:09.539
Well, like...

30:11.310 --> 30:12.754
CSI
and
Law & Order,
all that.

30:12.850 --> 30:14.420
No, no. Like a...

30:15.600 --> 30:16.760
a real one.

30:19.810 --> 30:20.765
Have you?

30:21.860 --> 30:22.815
Yeah.

30:23.110 --> 30:24.020
Once.

30:27.820 --> 30:29.026
What was that like?

30:31.070 --> 30:32.116
Quiet.

30:34.750 --> 30:36.957
Not silent or anything, just...

30:37.830 --> 30:38.865
no excitement.

30:39.420 --> 30:42.036
No big noise.

30:42.210 --> 30:45.122
Just cops walking around doing their jobs.

30:46.720 --> 30:47.789
Like it was nothin'.

30:50.720 --> 30:51.789
How old were you?

30:52.550 --> 30:53.551
Seventeen.

30:57.140 --> 30:58.630
What was the crime?

31:02.980 --> 31:04.015
Suicide.

31:12.570 --> 31:13.650
You were there.

31:17.370 --> 31:18.280
