31:59.080 --> 32:00.365
[students laughing]

32:02.370 --> 32:04.838
So you could help me
touch just one person?

32:05.920 --> 32:06.909
What?

32:07.000 --> 32:08.080
I doubt it.

32:08.880 --> 32:11.292
People l/ke you don ’1' make selﬂess moves.

32:11.380 --> 32:14.543
Oh, my God, dude, this shit is crazy!

32:16.140 --> 32:19.428
"Today I am wearing lacy black underwear

32:19.520 --> 32:22.341
with the sole purpose of knowing
that I am wearing it."

32:22.440 --> 32:26.604
-I wonder who's the skank who wrote this!
