and everybody ends up laughing.

33:41.060 --> 33:44.803
"I've got skin, miles and miles of skin.

33:45.190 --> 33:49.183
I've got skin to cover all my thoughts
like Saran Wrap."

33:49.810 --> 33:51.641
[Tony]
I can see her through the window.

33:53.820 --> 33:56.027
She walks up to the door,
she leaves this box.

33:56.820 --> 33:57.980
And goes.

34:00.080 --> 34:01.069
I didn't get up.

34:03.080 --> 34:05.321
