34:17.630 --> 34:19.211
I should have talked to her.

34:20.220 --> 34:21.255
But...

34:23.640 --> 34:25.050
Look, I liked Hannah.

34:26.230 --> 34:27.549
She was a friend.

34:27.640 --> 34:29.688
