or stare at her tits.

34:38.240 --> 34:40.231
And so I always got to hear about it...

34:40.820 --> 34:42.822
and on that particular day,
I didn't want to deal,

34:42.910 --> 34:44.366
so I let her walk away.

34:48.160 --> 34:49.286
Jesus, Tony.

34:52.130 --> 34:53.165
Half hour...

34:53.670 --> 34:55.376
forty-five minutes later,

34:55.460 --> 34:58.372
