How could you do that to me?

36:55.080 --> 36:56.286
The poem?

36:56.380 --> 36:59.452
I did you a favor, Hannah.
You're a beautiful poet.

36:59.630 --> 37:01.166
Your work deserved to be heard.

37:01.510 --> 37:04.252
