and know that I was right.

37:10.850 --> 37:14.229
What you wrote, you can't teach that.
You have to live it.

37:14.310 --> 37:16.722
Well, it's my life, Ryan, it's not yours.

37:17.400 --> 37:18.389
Get your own.

37:22.070 --> 37:24.026
There was a path the whole time?

37:24.860 --> 37:26.737
We could have just walked up there?

37:26.820 --> 37:29.152
Yes. But what's the fun in that?

37:30.240 --> 37:32.492
Everything you told me,
you could have told me anywhere.

37:32.950 --> 37:34.247
In Monet's the other night.

37:34.330 --> 37:36.286
Would you have been ready to hear it?

37:37.290 --> 37:38.279
Yeah.

37:41.050 --> 37:42.449
No. I don't know.

37:46.840 --> 37:48.250
I wish I had known, though.

37:50.010 --> 37:51.966
Why you cared so much about Hannah.

37:53.430 --> 37:55.057
I kept trying to figure it out.

37:58.650 --> 37:59.639
I thought maybe...

38:01.730 --> 38:03.937
I thought maybe you were in love with her.

38:06.240 --> 38:07.559
Clay...

38:07.660 --> 38:09.059
you know I'm gay, right?

38:13.660 --> 38:14.649
What?

38:17.670 --> 38:20.491
