38:25.260 --> 38:26.830
I don't think everyone knows.

38:26.930 --> 38:28.124
A lot of people know it.

38:30.430 --> 38:31.840
Wait, wait, wait, wait.

38:31.930 --> 38:33.886
Did you think that I was, like...

38:34.890 --> 38:36.175
just friends with Ryan?

38:37.940 --> 38:39.589
Well, yeah, I guess so.

38:42.860 --> 38:46.398
You think I would be friends
with a guy like Ryan.

38:47.490 --> 38:50.698
Yeah, would think you would be
'cause apparently you went out.

38:50.780 --> 38:53.362
They're different things. Trust me.

38:57.500 --> 38:59.456
So that guy Brad...

38:59.540 --> 39:01.622
is he your boyfriend now?

39:01.710 --> 39:03.621
I hope he's still my boyfriend.

39:03.710 --> 39:06.338
He's been pretty annoyed lately because...

39:07.510 --> 39:10.081
I've been spending all my time
with another guy.

39:13.050 --> 39:14.096
You.

39:15.560 --> 39:16.458
Oh.

39:16.560 --> 39:17.424
Right.

39:19.310 --> 39:22.393
You mean with the tapes and all,
not in a romantic way.

39:24.320 --> 39:25.309
Sure.

39:30.150 --> 39:31.356
[Alex]
A/eX Standall.

39:31.450 --> 39:34.078
S-T-A-N-D-A-L-L.

39:35.740 --> 39:38.322
Yes. It's filled. Ready to go.

39:38.750 --> 39:42.163
Okay, with this, you want to take one
every night before bed,

39:42.250 --> 39:44.081
with water, with or without food.

39:44.210 --> 39:45.541
This one can make you dizzy--

39:45.630 --> 39:47.837
I know. I've been taking it
for a while now.

39:48.510 --> 39:49.465
Oh.

39:49.550 --> 39:50.835
We have this as new.

39:50.970 --> 39:52.506
I used to go to Walplex.

39:54.180 --> 39:57.263
I could have them send
your history over, if you like.

39:57.350 --> 39:59.136
Yeah, that'd be great, thank you.

40:08.570 --> 40:10.276
-There you go.
-Thanks.

40:15.200 --> 40:16.235
I, uh...

40:17.450 --> 40:18.781
I was friends with Hannah.

40:21.830 --> 40:23.115
You were?

40:23.370 --> 40:25.076
Yeah. Um...

40:25.170 --> 40:27.126
I'm really sorry about what happened.

40:30.550 --> 40:31.619
Thank you, Alex.

40:32.590 --> 40:33.579
Yeah.

40:43.810 --> 40:44.720
Thank you.

41:07.540 --> 41:09.952
Apparently your mom called my dad.

41:10.920 --> 41:12.080
Oh, Jesus.

41:12.170 --> 41:13.967
My mom. I'll text her.

41:14.050 --> 41:17.884
We do not need that particular
hysterical phone call at this moment.

41:17.970 --> 41:20.552
Maybe if you didn't keep all those
secrets from her--

41:20.640 --> 41:22.676
Oh, fuck you, with your secrets.

41:24.980 --> 41:25.969
[engine starts]

41:26.060 --> 41:27.106
Could I, uh...

41:29.400 --> 41:31.140
Could I get those tapes back sometime?

41:39.240 --> 41:40.229
Sure thing.

41:48.250 --> 41:50.741
So, what, was this your plan
the whole time?

41:50.920 --> 41:52.876
Maybe I helped it along, but...

41:52.960 --> 41:55.508
I knew sooner or later
you'd want the tapes back.

41:56.680 --> 41:58.079
-You knew?
-Yeah.

41:59.890 --> 42:01.300
You haven't heard yours yet.

42:13.610 --> 42:14.679
It's delicious, but...

42:15.320 --> 42:16.605
not another bite.

42:20.370 --> 42:21.359
Thank you.

42:23.450 --> 42:24.906
This was a good idea.

42:29.080 --> 42:30.206
[girl giggles]

42:32.420 --> 42:33.910
[chuckles] Oh.

42:34.710 --> 42:36.337
Honey, you can't do that.

42:36.920 --> 42:38.080
I'm so sorry.

42:38.180 --> 42:39.579
-Oh, no.
-She's totally fine.

42:39.720 --> 42:41.927
He was due for a new hairstyle anyway.

42:43.600 --> 42:44.589
What's your name?

42:45.730 --> 42:47.937
