42:48.020 --> 42:49.009
Sarah.

42:49.100 --> 42:50.089
Sarah.

42:50.610 --> 42:52.009
You're very cute, Sarah.

42:52.570 --> 42:53.969
Say thank you, Sarah.

42:54.070 --> 42:55.105
No.

42:55.740 --> 42:58.231
Sarah. That's not nice.

42:58.570 --> 43:01.403
Oh, please, don't worry about it.
I have a daughter too.

43:01.530 --> 43:04.442
No wonder you're such a pro.
How old is she?

43:05.040 --> 43:07.201
-Seventeen.
-Seventeen.

43:07.330 --> 43:08.911
Yeah, it flies by.

43:09.000 --> 43:12.834
Before you know it,
she'll be applying for colleges.

43:14.380 --> 43:16.166
Hannah's already looking.

43:17.050 --> 43:18.665
Hannah's such a pretty name.

43:20.340 --> 43:21.716
She wants to go to New York.

43:24.060 --> 43:25.004
Good luck.

43:26.100 --> 43:27.510
[mother] Let's go back to dinner.

43:28.180 --> 43:30.011
