It’s a horr/b/e story, Matt.

43:30.520 --> 43:32.181
She was a beautiful...

43:33.270 --> 43:35.522
sweet girl, and she's gone.

43:36.780 --> 43:39.271
Of course, we're supposed
to tear her apart.

43:40.990 --> 43:43.618
Go after her reputation, her boyfriends,

43:43.780 --> 43:45.782
anything she's ever written or said.

43:45.870 --> 43:48.247
So don't do it. Don't go after her.

43:49.660 --> 43:51.491
You always said that's why you did law.

43:51.580 --> 43:54.242
If it didn't always serve justice,
it could serve the truth.

43:55.210 --> 43:56.199
Right?

43:56.880 --> 43:58.120
So find out the truth.

44:00.420 --> 44:02.001
What if it hurts our son?

44:03.010 --> 44:04.841
I believe he'll survive.

44:05.260 --> 44:06.466
[car approaches]

44:08.220 --> 44:09.847
