44:12.810 --> 44:15.017
You think that Tony's a good influence?

44:16.440 --> 44:19.068
My sense of him is
that he's a very good influence.

44:19.900 --> 44:21.811
But that's not our concern
at the moment, right?

44:21.900 --> 44:23.561
Nope. I know.

44:24.490 --> 44:25.696
I am on board.

44:27.290 --> 44:28.359
[door opens]

44:40.210 --> 44:41.370
I'm sorry.

44:41.470 --> 44:42.505
I'm...

44:43.840 --> 44:44.886
really.

44:46.640 --> 44:49.848
Tony and I had to talk,
