for a few minutes!

46:07.180 --> 46:08.499
Should we move?

46:08.800 --> 46:09.789
What?

46:09.890 --> 46:12.211
Should we move?
Should we go somewhere and start new?

46:14.560 --> 46:15.549
And...

46:16.390 --> 46:17.345
give up the store?

46:17.440 --> 46:20.728
I'll give up the store,
give up the house, everything...

46:23.030 --> 46:24.065
if I have you.

46:25.570 --> 46:26.730
But you do.

46:28.160 --> 46:29.309
You do have me.

46:30.950 --> 46:31.939
Okay.

46:32.540 --> 46:33.575
Good.

46:38.370 --> 46:39.530
-[glass tips over]
-Shit.

46:40.580 --> 46:41.581
Damn it.

46:47.130 --> 46:49.337
I thought you had
poetry workshop tonight.

46:49.430 --> 46:50.465
Didn't go.

46:51.760 --> 46:53.250
Never going back.

46:53.640 --> 46:54.709
And we need to move.

46:56.850 --> 46:59.899
Four hundred and thirty a month,
and that's before the false alarms,

46:59.980 --> 47:01.800
which they charge you for,
even though it's their fault.

47:01.900 --> 47:05.563
You should have told me you canceled.
I was on hold with them for an hour!

47:05.690 --> 47:07.351
